snippet.title: Canceled Blur 2 Prototype - Exploring All Courses
snippet.description:
All drivable tracks from the leaked Blur 2 Prototype dated 9th November 2010 intended for documentational purposes. Timecodes below.
Meant as an additional companion piece to this (german) scripted video featuring the history of Blur's canceled successor: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TDn7J1qQZHM


Timecodes:
0:00 Titlescreen
0:07 Dubai
10:26 Hong Kong
19:15 LA City
26:07 LA Freeway
31:36 Miami
39:10 North Africa
45:08 Odessa
53:29 Ski Resort
1:05:18 Detroit
1:13:50 some bonus stuff 





Die Beschreibung war mal deutsch. Aber dann kam Reddit und alles änderte sich.

 -

Streaming: https://mixer.com/altf4games
